name: Donyoribo @Ignister
desc: During damage calculation when your "@Ignister" monster is attacked: You can discard this card; you take no damage from that battle. When your opponent would take damage due to the effect of an "@Ignister" monster or an "A.I." Spell/Trap: You can banish this card from the GY (even during the Damage Step): Double the damage that would be inflicted. You can only use each effect of "Donyoribo @Ignister" once per turn.
